  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Smoking Gun </strong>is a Wild West vertical shoot ’em up that fuses classic arcade action with gunslinger style. Ride into Hickstown as an Arizona Ranger, dodge waves of outlaw fire, collect power-ups, upgrade your arsenal, and take down deadly bosses in a retro-inspired showdown for justice.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984340/extras/c21cfd15fdf202a5821cf1db223f3f9a.poster.avif?t=1774470248\" width=500 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984340/extras/c21cfd15fdf202a5821cf1db223f3f9a.webm?t=1774470248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984340/extras/c21cfd15fdf202a5821cf1db223f3f9a.mp4?t=1774470248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wild West shmup action</strong> — A rare western take on the vertical shoot ’em up formula. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade your arsenal </strong>— Collect gold, ammo, and power-ups to strengthen your weapons and improve your loadout.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade-style challenge</strong> — Tough enemies, limited saves, and reflex-driven combat inspired by old-school arcade shooters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boss showdowns</strong> — Face dangerous outlaw leaders in intense, bullet-filled battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Score-chasing replayability</strong> — Improve your runs, master enemy patterns, and push for higher scores.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Modern visuals, retro spirit</strong> — Classic arcade design enhanced with modern effects and presentation.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984340/extras/cc80fd997c4dd30de8d17c49a0105243.poster.avif?t=1774470248\" width=500 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984340/extras/cc80fd997c4dd30de8d17c49a0105243.webm?t=1774470248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984340/extras/cc80fd997c4dd30de8d17c49a0105243.mp4?t=1774470248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
